name: Breeze Rider Essence
description: Magical dust from a breezerider. Rixt thinks this is what gives them their ability to fly. He might be interested in this.

name: Encryption Crystal
description: This crystal contains information that will help Frazz gain control of Bauxite Alchemicals faster.

name: Orrian Energy Source
description: This energy source could be the key to something...

name: Bittersweet Omnomberry
description: A special variety of Omnomberry that Byanca is particularly interested in.

name: Harpy Feather
description: A feather plucked from a harpy. Wode might find these useful.

name: Explosive Powder
description: Explosive power stolen from Separatists. Jahr Duskrend would probably want this.

name: Jotun Runestone
description: Albin Chronicler is very interested in these.

name: Discarded Sylvari Tool
description: Brannen outside of Caer Brier would probably want these.

name: Blue Wurm Husk
description:
An odd blue wurm husk
<c=@flavor>"This may have come from a Bug!"</c>

name: Tuning Crystal
description: These crystal shards were mined from the rocks around Ulta Metamagicals. Tekki is using them to tune her upgraded asura gates.

name: Cursed Pirate Artifact
description: Priory explorers have been searching for these.

name: Jellyfish Remains
description: A real quaggan treat!

name: Crabmeat
description: Hunk of crabmeat only enjoyed by quaggan. Doolsileep could make something tasty with this.

name: Meat Hunk
description: A large hunk of meat. Chef Mestergruff of Mennerheim might want this.

name: Firefly Essence
description: The hylek have been known to concoct powerful explosives by processing remains of luminescent insects.

name: Blackvein Fiber
description: Coating a weapon in these plant leaves will infect wounds delivered by them. Any Seraph in Harathi Highlands could use this.

name: Slice of Grub Meat
description: Forager Sneckit in Skrittsburgh Hillstead collects this meat so it can feed skritt throughout Skrittsburgh.

name: Seraph Supplies
description: These supplies were likely stolen by bandits and should be returned to Seraph Goran in The Wendon Steps.

name: Whetstone
description: Broil Cane's friends and members of the Companions could use these whetstones in their war against the centaur.

name: Green Stinkhorn
description: These pungent mushrooms are being harvested by the Durmand Priory, to be extracted and and turned into tonics that cure all kinds of ailments.

name: Undamaged Power-Bauble
description: Twitchok in Skrittsburgh Tunnels is collecting these.

name: Bandit Documents
description: These documents contain detailed information on the bandit activity in the region. The Seraph would be very interested in this intelligence.

name: Red Summoning Stone
description: A red stone that's warm to the touch. Scholar Inka is using these for her experiments.

name: Blue Summoning Stone
description: A cracked blue stone that's cold to the touch. Scholar Inka is using these for her experiments.

name: Black Summoning Stone
description: A black, brimstone-scented stone. Scholar Inka is using these for her experiments.

name: Kodan Supplies
description: Recovered supplies from Blue Ice Shining. Return these to Guard Splintering Serenity.

name: Volcanic Rock
description: A shard of pitch black volcanic rock. It is extremely sharp. Sangdo Swiftwing is interested in these.

name: Scrap Metal
description: Oddly marked scrap metal taken from the steam creatures.

name: Chunk of Unrefined Dredge Ore
description: Priory Arcanist Dotta in the north of Dostoev Sky Peak is breaking down this ore.

name: Treasure
description: Return these to Admiral Clarinda Demard at Forvar's Landing.

name: Explosive Powder
description: A special explosive that destroys steam creatures. Remember, don't use too much.

name: Frozen Fish
description: Guardian Infinite Mind in Groznev Delve is looking for these.

name: Moa Meat
description: Guardian Infinite Mind in Groznev Delve is looking for these.

name: Asuran Relic
description: Explorer Cryptcutter from Rata Pten in Mount Maelstrom is collecting these.

name: Chunk of Dolyak Meat
description: Enduring Protector is looking for meat to feed his refugees.

name: Barracuda Meat
description: Hunk of barracuda meat enjoyed by kodan. Enduring Protector is looking to feed the refugees with this.

name: Skritt Artifact
description: A forgetten artifact the skritt left behind in the rush to escape the risen. Just what Crusader Aisling is looking for.
